data.description: Great opportunity to buy this 1.5 story fixer upper located in Cleveland, OH and sitting on a 35x119 lot with a detached garage. The interior has 1366 sq. ft. with 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, living room, foyer and dining room, plus a full basement.  Property is lender-owned, being sold as-is, and seller makes no representations or warranties.
